	<text xml:lang="la">
		<body>
			<div>
				<p>
					<s n="1" xml:lang="la" type="auto">S.</s>
					<s n="2" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Cuius me literę medullitus exhilarant, amice incomparabilis, tu, mihi crede, precipuus es.</s>
					<s n="3" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Percepi non ita longo intervallo ternas ex te maxima profecto voluptate; dolui autem quasdam antea ad me datas aut interiisse aut interceptas esse.</s>
					<s n="4" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Respondi ad proximas brevissime sperans te coram illico me visurum, id quod et iam nunc factum esset, nisi aeris inclementia tum et asperum iter obstitisset; differenda igitur peregrinatio mea erit usque ad proximum ver.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="5" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Interim cogitabis, amabo, quomodo frater tuus cum uxore et prole reliquum vitę instituat.</s>
					<s n="6" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Hic non solum in periculo, sed etiam in sordibus vivere mihi videor, quamquam dominus ab insidiis multorum me hactenus servavit.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="7" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Quid autem cum piis futurum sit (humano more loquor) nescitur; scimus autem hoc sęculum minitari multas turbas.</s>
					<s n="8" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l303">Magdeburgenses</placeName> Interimicę constitutioni nondum subscribunt.</s>
					<s n="9" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><persName type="citizen_name" ref="p18250">Dux Mauricius Saxo</persName> est quid grande contra eos conatus, sed re infecta, ut audio, ab obsidione destitit.</s>
					<s n="10" xml:lang="la" type="auto" ana="salute">Tu vale in aurea libertate cum preclarissimis fratribus, quibus singulis salutem ex me efflictim dices.</s>
					<s n="11" xml:lang="de" type="auto">Ex <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l245">Kauffburna</placeName> 4. decembris 1550.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="12" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Scire aveo, ut valeant domini consules, ut <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p8498">Theodorius</persName> in arundine et an <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p2916">Schertlerus</persName> adhuc <placeName ref="l28">Basileae</placeName> hereat.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="13" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Tuus <persName ref="p8354">G[eorgius] L[aetus</persName>].</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="14" xml:lang="la" type="auto"><placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l18">Augustę</placeName> comicia celebrantur perpetua; nemo autem ordinum imperii novit, quis tandem finis talium rerum erit.</s>
					<s n="15" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Dicunt quidam nobis propediem plures nascituros reges, imperatorem <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p18538">Carolum</persName> diadema fratri <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p18477">Ferdinando</persName> cessurum, <persName type="citizen_name" ref="p18575">Philippum</persName> autem, principem <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l875">Hispaniarum</placeName>, in regem <placeName type="citizen_name" ref="l425">Romanum</placeName> coronandum.</s>
					<s n="16" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Reliqua ostendunt belli faciem.</s>
				</p>
				<p>
					<s n="17" xml:lang="la" type="auto">Preclarissimo viro domino <persName ref="p495" type="citizen_name">Heinricho Bullingero</persName>, antistiti <placeName ref="l587" type="auto_name">Tigur[in]o</placeName> spectabili.</s>
				</p>
			</div>
